.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Transport: skateboard, helicopter, tram, bike, boat
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Beverage:coffee
6. Transport:tram == Pet:bird
7. Color:yellow == Transport:helicopter
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Transport:boat is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Transport:helicopter
12. Transport:skateboard == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == Transport:bike
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Transport:boat is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Transport		|   helicopter	|    boat	|  tram	|    bike	|   skateboard	|
